'''Snickers''' (2002 - 2022) was an American beagle. 

==Life==
Snickers was born in San Diego, California as the result of his father barking up the "right tree." His owner was Richard "Ricky" Lester (born 1956), a flight attendant.

==Footnotes==
* Life played on January 8, 2022. 
* Obtained "Ordinary" ribbon.
